  * Add any/submitted-origin.diff from Andreas Schwab to forbid the use
    of $ORIGIN in privileged programs. Add any/cvs-audit-suid.diff to
    only load SUID audit objects in SUID binaries. Fix CVE-2010-3847.
    Closes: #600667.
