    sys/user.h on alpha.  Closes: #480295.
  * patches/any/submitted-user_h.diff: don't include linux/user.h from
    sys/user.h.  Closes: #480093.
  * patches/hppa/submitted-fesetenv.diff: fix fesetenv() on hppa with
    gcc-4.3.
